Class CollectionUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • CollectionUtils

  • public final class CollectionUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains various useful methods related to manipulating collections and arrays of data.

        public static <K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,V extends java.lang.Comparable<V>> java.util.SortedMap<V,java.util.Set<K>> reverseMap(java.util.Map<K,V> map)
